    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>As a swift action, a scyphozoan can make one of her prehensile tentacles secrete acid; her unarmed strikes with that tentacle count as having the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.equipment.tXg2Qct6wWKXvzFW]{Corrosive} weapon fusion, except the ability is not magical. While the effect is activated, the scyphozoan is considered armed, and the attack doesn’t count as archaic, but the scyphozoan cannot hold an item in that tentacle.</p>\n<p>Starting at 3rd level, a scyphozoan adds 1-1/2 × her character level to the damage while the effect is activated. A scyphozoan can deactivate the effect as a swift action.</p>\n<p><em>Damage calculation is already set to account the additional damage of 1/2&nbsp;<span>× their character level, beyond the damage provided by their normal Weapon Specialization damage.</span></em></p>"
